## Product API

### 이리내 추가 요청

POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "이리내",
  "price": 10000000,
  "imageUrl": "#"
}

### 전체 상품 조회 요청

GET http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

### 특정 상품 조회 요청

GET http://localhost:8080/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 주노 수정 요청 (가격 수정)

PUT http://localhost:8080/products/6
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "주노",
  "price": 150000,
  "imageUrl": "#"
}

### 제리 삭제 요청

DELETE http://localhost:8080/products/2
Content-Type: application/json

## Member API

### 전체 멤버 조회

GET http://localhost:8080/members
Content-Type: application/json

### 특정 멤버 조회

GET http://localhost:8080/members/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 멤버 생성 (회원가입)

POST http://localhost:8080/members/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "gitchan@gmail.com",
  "password": "gitchan_coding"
}

### Cart Item API

### 장바구니 아이템 목록 조회

GET http://localhost:8080/cart-items
Authorization: Basic YUBhLmNvbToxMjM0

### 장바구니 아이템 추가

POST http://localhost:8080/cart-items
Authorization: Basic YUBhLmNvbToxMjM0
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 4,
  "quantity": 3
}

### 장바구니 아이템 수량 변경

PATCH http://localhost:8080/cart-items/1
Authorization: Basic YUBhLmNvbToxMjM0
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

### 장바구니 내 아이템 구매

POST http://localhost:8080/pay
Authorization: Basic YUBhLmNvbToxMjM0
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartItemIds": [
    {
      "cartItemId": 1
    },
    {
      "cartItemId": 3
    }
  ],
  "originalPrice": 52000,
  "points": 100
}

